TinyFugue with the Lua patch 
============================
I found out about it via: 
- http://forums.lusternia.com/index.php?showtopic=14128

Follow those directions.


Lua libraries That Need To Be Installed By You
==============================================

Luasql (with sqlite3 support builtin):
- http://www.keplerproject.org/luasql/
--> On Ubuntu 9.10: "apt-get install liblua5.1-sql-sqlite3-2"



Included External Libraries
===========================

lunit (for running tests, optional):
- http://www.mroth.net/lunit/
- License: docs/lunit/LICENSE